{"title":"BOTTOMS","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"drip-basics-sweatpants-f","title":"DRIP BASICS SWEATPANTS – F","description":"\u003cp\u003e420 GSM.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eCotton fleece fabric.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eCombed \u0026amp; bio washed.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eOnly for female.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eDesigned for ultimate comfort and effortless style.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eStraight-fit joggers made from luxurious 350 GSM fabric.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eOffers a soft feel and superior durability.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eFeatures a convenient back pocket for added utility.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eBlends practicality with everyday streetwear style.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eSuitable for casual days or elevated street looks.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\nCare Guide\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the jogger inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eStore the jogger in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\nCore Features\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eJoggers with 420 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for comfortable and versatile wear.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eBack pocket for convenient storage.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eElasticated waist to adjust for a custom fit and added style.\u003c\/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46853861638298,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46853861671066,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853861703834,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46853861736602,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46853861769370,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46853861802138,"sku":"bottoms","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/IMG_5633_11zon.jpg?v=1768930731"},{"product_id":"black-basic-bottom","title":"BLACK BASIC BOTTOM","description":"\u003cp\u003e MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M BOTTOMS.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n420 GSM TAPED COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e\nCOMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e\nSTRAIGHT BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e\nJET BLACK MINIMAL DESIGN\u003cbr\u003e\nUNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCrafted from 420 GSM premium taped cotton fleece for a dense, structured feel with long-term durability.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStraight baggy silhouette delivers relaxed comfort with a modern streetwear edge.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClean blank finish makes it easy to pair with graphic tees, hoodies, or elevated essentials.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eJet black tone offers a timeless, sharp look suitable for both casual and styled outfits.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTaped fleece construction adds structure while maintaining flexibility and everyday comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePerfect for all seasons, offering warmth, breathability, and a premium heavyweight presence.\u003c\/li\u00