fabric weight suitable for year-round wear.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885005590682,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885005623450,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885005656218,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885005688986,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885005721754,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885005754522,"sku":"DS SIGNATURE SWEATPANTS","price":1799.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/IMG_5631_11zon_1.webp?v=1772291602"},{"product_id":"luxe-bottoms","title":"LUXE BOTTOMS","description":"\u003cp\u003e MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M BOTTOMS.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e 420 GSM SOFT FLEECE LINING\u003cbr\u003e COMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e PREMIUM 100% COTTON MATERIAL\u003cbr\u003e BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e EMBROIDERED LOGO ON FRONT\u003cbr\u003e BELT LOOP FOR KEYS OR LIGHTER\u003cbr\u003e ZIPPER POCKETS FOR SECURE STORAGE\u003cbr\u003e UNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eCrafted from 420 GSM heavy-duty cotton fleece with soft internal lining for superior comfort, warmth, and durability.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight-cut baggy silhouette designed for relaxed comfort and versatile streetwear styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eElegant front embroidery adds subtle premium branding and refined streetwear appeal.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSmooth, reliable YKK zipper pockets secure belongings while maintaining a clean look.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eAdditional sleek back pocket with refined piping work enhances aesthetic and functionality.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eFunctional belt loop allows for keys, a lighter, or small essentials — combining utility with style.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003ePerfect combination of elevated minimalism, craftsmanship, and street-lux comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the sweatpants inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and embroidery integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to maintain shape and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eJoggers constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a durable and substantial feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for comfortable, versatile wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBack pocket for convenient storage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eElasticated waist for a custom fit and added style.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey backing ensures all-day comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885006213274,"sku":"Reign3","price":1998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885006246042,"sku":"Reign3","price":1998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885006278810,"sku":"Reign3","price":1998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885006311578,"sku":"Reign3","price":1998.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885006344346,"sku":"Reign3","price":1998.0