 modern streetwear styling.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft hand feel with a premium matte finish for elevated comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eVersatile essential that balances function, comfort, and attitude.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eMachine wash the sweatpants inside out with like colors.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUse cold water to preserve fabric quality and print integrity.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStore in a cool, dry place to maintain shape and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e \u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003eSweatpants constructed with 420 GSM fabric for a substantial and durable feel.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit for relaxed, all-day comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eUnisex article suitable for diverse body types and style preferences.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eElasticated waistband for adjustable fit and ease of wear.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eBack pocket for added utility.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eSoft, breathable jersey construction ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/li\u003e \u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885007622298,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2148.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885007655066,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2148.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885007687834,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2148.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885007720602,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":2148.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885007753370,"sku":"Reign4(-Copy 